data.description: Welcome to 305 E Main St, located in the HEART of Stockbridge. This Stately 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home boasts nearly 3000 sq ft of living space above grade! This property features a very deep, detached 2-car garage with abundant overhead storage and sits on a good sized, fenced in, city lot. As you walk in the home, experience the convenience of a mudroom directly off the driveway. The kitchen is equipped with an abundant amount of elegant hickory cabinets and sleek stainless steel appliances, along with a small bar top area. Enjoy the fresh feel of new flooring and paint in most of the home. The bedrooms are impressively spacious. But wait, there is MORE! There is a HUGE finished third story loft that would be a cozy bedroom space, mancave area or kids playroom! You will LOVE this space! Modern amenities include an on-demand water heater, a 200 amp electrical service, and a newer boiler. For added comfort and efficiency, each floor is equipped with its own thermostat, helping to keep heating costs low. This beautiful home combines comfort with elegance in a superb living space. At a little over $100/sq ft of finished living space ABOVE GRADE, you cannot beat this deal! Schedule your showing TODAY!
